Table

mj_table.Rd

This tag allows you to display table and filled it with data.

mj_table(df)

Arguments

df

a data.frame.

See also

https://mjml.io/documentation/#mjml-table

Examples

mj_ml(
  mj_body(
    mj_column(
      mj_table(mtcars)
    )
  )
)
